name: Invalid APP_ID header

steps.name: Given I have a new user data located at "features/data/user_data1.json" with generated email
When I send a POST request to "/user/create" with app id: "6636324525a5b823ed8a1121434"
Then the response status code should be 403
And the response should contain error "APP_ID_NOT_EXIST" with value "APP_ID_NOT_EXIST"

fullName: Api testing for create endpoint: Invalid APP_ID header
